Title: Bvlgari Blv EDP  -  75 ml(For Women)
Description: The Bvlgari Blv exudes an intoxication through a combination of notes that leave you with an alluring yet complex fragrance. The ingredients are hand-picked for the versatile and unpredictable woman who packs her bag for an unknown destination seeking a memorable journey. Perfumer Alberto Morillas developed this enigmatic luxury Eau de Parfum for the fashion house of Bvlgari. Elegantly wrapped in contrasting layers of floral hints and woody accents, this perfume envelopes your senses with a calm aroma. The musky tone makes its presence felt, much like the charming woman who leaves her impression wherever she goes. A zesty top note of ginger and acacia makes way for a whiff of fresh fragrant wisteria with sweet and nutty flax. This leads you to a scintillating base note of sandalwood, musk, black locust and vanilla, reminiscent of a wild nature - generous and boundless. The harmonious blend of these scents transports you to a walk in the woods on a crisp spring morning. The free spirited woman can wear this fragrance at any time and bask in its refreshing essence. Bottled in a sophisticated square glass vial, she can dab on a few drops of mesmerising aqua that takes her on an adventure of a lifetime.

It will improve your skin texture, elasticity and gradually restore the moisture balance of your skin.Sandal Wood is an antibiotic element that keeps your skin free from harmful virus and bacteria. It helps to reduce scars, pimples and softens it by moisturising. It is being used for centuries in Ayurveda for skin repair. Graham and Dinah started an extensive research and finally created the legendary Oil of Olay Beauty Fluid. Today, Olay is a well-known and trusted brand that promises the dainty ladies healthy and beautiful skin. Olay delivers products that are safe for its customers by ensuring that each product manufactured undergoes a thorough quality test. Celebrate beauty and pamper your skin with Olay. Olay Total Effects 7 in One Cream + Serum Duo SPF 15 Get well-moisturized skin and glowing complexion with this Olay Total Effects 7 in One Cream + Serum Duo SPF 15 that nourishes your skin and prevents dryness. Claims This product comes with ceam and SPF 15 that protect your skin from the harmful rays of the sun and keep it in good condition. Features and Benefits - The cream and the serum fight the seven signs of ageing to give you younger looking skin. - Use this product everyday to remove tan and get even skin tone. - Total Effects 7 in One Cream + Serum Duo SPF 15 brightens your skin and gives it a healthy glow by reducing dullness and minimizing pores. - Use this cream and serum duo everyday to reduce fine lines and wrinkles and improve your skin's texture. Directions Use this face care product on a clean face and neck twice a day to see visible results. Warnings Avoid contact with the eye area. If the cream gets into eyes then rinse thoroughly with water. Incase of any occurrence of skin and eye irritations, please discontinue using this product. Keep this product out of reach of children.
